	<article class="post-639346 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-legal tag-banking-and-financial-institutions tag-brazil tag-credit-and-debt tag-interest-rates tag-pawnbroking tag-personal-finances tag-rousseff-dilma per-rousseff-dilma des-banking-and-financial-institutions des-credit-and-debt des-interest-rates des-pawnbroking des-personal-finances geo-brazil news_keywords-banking-and-finance news_keywords-brazil news_keywords-debt-2 news_keywords-dilma-rousseff news_keywords-interest-rate news_keywords-pawnbroker news_keywords-personal-finance" id="post-639346">
